{"tid":2210682,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港大公共衛生學院實驗室14環境樣本呈陽性　41人須檢疫 (22:53)","createTime":"2020-09-20T14:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T18:36:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d379135792cd362198edf2952438e9a931de0ed2","tid":2210682,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T14:54:58.000Z","msg":"港大公共衛生學院實驗室28歲女研究員確診新型冠狀病毒，院方採集實驗室環境樣本化驗。衛生防護中心今日（20日）回覆本報表示，採集的37個環境樣本中，有14個樣本對新型冠狀病毒呈陽性反應，中心已安排41名於實驗室工作的密切接觸者檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n此外，衛生防護中心向實驗室提供330個樣本瓶作新冠病毒檢測，至回覆時沒有陽性個案，流行病學調查及化驗仍在進行中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200920/s00001/1600613163196/%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e-%e6%b8%af%e5%a4%a7%e5%85%ac%e5%85%b1%e8%a1%9b%e7%94%9f%e5%ad%b8%e9%99%a2%e5%af%a6%e9%a9%97%e5%ae%a414%e7%92%b0%e5%a2%83%e6%a8%a3%e6%9c%ac%e5%91%88%e9%99%bd%e6%80%a7-41%e4%ba%ba%e9%a0%88%e6%aa%a2%e7%96%ab?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200920%2Fs00001%2F1600613163196%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e-%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%2585%25b1%25e8%25a1%259b%25e7%2594%259f%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e9%2599%25a2%25e5%25af%25a6%25e9%25a9%2597%25e5%25ae%25a414%25e7%2592%25b0%25e5%25a2%2583%25e6%25a8%25a3%25e6%259c%25ac%25e5%2591%2588%25e9%2599%25bd%25e6%2580%25a7-41%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e9%25a0%2588%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e7%2596%25ab%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2OmuSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=16443e65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200920%2Fs00001%2F1600613163196%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e-%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%2585%25b1%25e8%25a1%259b%25e7%2594%259f%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e9%2599%25a2%25e5%25af%25a6%25e9%25a9%2597%25e5%25ae%25a414%25e7%2592%25b0%25e5%25a2%2583%25e6